Hi Matt,

Stack just brought up that you need to turn off the extractors.
If you want embeds (images, frames, etc.) than leave extractors on, setup max-hops to 1 and enable 
additionalScopeFocus and set max-embed-hops.

Also, if you have 7M URLs from ~7M different hosts that would require a lot of memory since for each 
host we need to create a separate queue. Therefore, we suggest that you change default 
QueueAssignmentPolicy to something like this 
http://crawler.archive.org/apidocs/org/archive/crawler/frontier/BucketQueueAssignmentPolicy.html

Let us know if this is working out for you.
Take care,
i.

